lou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katerina_Sakellaropoulou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katerina_Sakellaropoulou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The president of the Republic greeted one - one of the athletes found at the Presidential Palace, while photographed with both Greek missions.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999703489141645, \"rank\": 2.946190050016608e-05, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Typical was the moment when he spoke with the Olympic champion, Lefteris Petrounia, but also with the -of our two flag bearers at the Opening Ceremony - Antigone Drishbiotis. \\\"\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us go to Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999987321644, \"rank\": 9.565936561659274e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You also set this example of continuity.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Always be well and enjoy your daughters,\\\" the president of the Republic told the \\\"Lord of the Lilies\\\".\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw her.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They had a touching human dimension all of this.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very impressive\\\" she told Spyros Capralos about Antigone Drismiotis, who appeared moved, after her attempt at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyros_Capralos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Spyros Capralos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyros_Capralos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spyros_Capralos\"}, {\"begin\": 1296, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antigone\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.275906555221634e-21, \"text\": \"Antigone\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antigone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antigone\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See this post on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2743202173018943e-16, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See this post on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2743202173018943e-16, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is with great pleasure and pride that I welcome you to the Presidential Palace, to an event of recognition, on the part of the State, of your achievements, individual and collective, but above all your struggle, perseverance and fortitude.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_House\", \"score\": 0.9998817974598805, \"rank\": 0.00011821522039330288, \"text\": \"Presidential Palace\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_House\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_House\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have been distinguished in a field of noble chisel, where besides performance, the morale of athletes is valued and evaluated; field in which you all excel.\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loyalty to the cause, respect to the opponent, modesty, dignity, virtues that give the measure of well-being, acquire standing in each one of you.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every athlete, every athlete, in his individual effort faces challenges and adversities.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From the possible injuries to the mental pressure it undergoes in order to perform at a high level, as well as any deficiencies in preparation, the road to victory is sown with obstacles.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But for you nothing is a deterrent.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By subjecting the body to the spirit, without being intimidated by failures or defeats, you managed to reach the top.\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even more difficult is the way to the podium of disabled people.\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of Greece has followed your effort in awe, realizing how much strength and endurance it is necessary to recruit an athlete who faces kinetic, sensory or other problems in order to devote himself to the extremely demanding organization of the Paralympic Games.\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2486, \"end\": 2492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.090645883448525e-11, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How determined and how willless.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those involved in these struggles, regardless of discrimination, deserve our unlimited admiration.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to congratulate you with my heart and thank you on behalf of all Greeks.\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loyal to the Olympic ideal, you have not only been accomplished individually, but have highlighted our country worldwide.\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are a brilliant example for our young people.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The moral integrity, self-discipline, hard work, and consistency you show in each step make up a standard of life that encourages and inspires.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wish you all the best.\\\"\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Katerina Sakellaropoulou said in her greeting to Greek athletes.\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3297, \"end\": 3321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katerina_Sakellaropoulou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katerina Sakellaropoulou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katerina_Sakellaropoulou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katerina_Sakellaropoulou\"}, {\"begin\": 3346, \"end\": 3351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999703489141645, \"rank\": 2.946190050016608e-05, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember that the President of the Republic will give \\\"present\\\" this afternoon to the great celebration of the UN \\\"Athens 20 years later\\\" that will take place at the Panathinaikos Stadium, for the Olympians, Paralympians and European Champions in Euro 2004!\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3473, \"end\": 3475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9808560195993072, \"rank\": 0.019508631133586498, \"text\": \"UN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 3477, \"end\": 3483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.241314860360977e-14, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athens Times  News about Greece and the World.\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3621, \"end\": 3627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.241314860360977e-14, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}, {\"begin\": 3646, \"end\": 3652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.090645883448525e-11, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}]}"